title: The One About Nightlife
description:
Bob and Monét are in a silly goofy mood this week. You won't want to miss this off the rails episode as they share stories from working nightlife and bicker about everything under the sun!
See Monét and Bob on tour this summer by going to bobandmonet.com !!
